data.persona: I come from the lower class. I do what I am told without question. I can not read. I have not seen my family in a long time.
data.description:
You are in the throne room.
ornate and luxurious, the throne room gleams with gold and precious jewels. Priceless painting of past kings line the sides. underneath a vaulted ceiling regal a red carpet connect the throne room entrance to the golden throne itself.
There's a golden throne, a priceless painting of past kings, a statue, a gold, a vaulted ceiling, a crown, a Curtain, a priceless painting, a window, a jewel, a sword, a Gold cup, a red carpet, and a banner here.
The queen and the king are here.

You are carrying nothing, and wearing a shirt and a sword.
